dct_description_sm: "Compiled by 512 Fd. survey coy., R.E., October 1941, from air photographs dated June, 1941. Names based on Italian town plan. Revised from air photographs dated October 1942 abd reorinted October, 1942."
"Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington D. C. 114559. 3-43. 1943."
Oriented with north toward the upper left.
Selected streets and buildings are named.
Also available on the Internet through the American Geographical Society Library Digital Map Collection.
